{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Freedom means that all of a sudden, I have all the food that I want.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then certain things started to appear in my head, and I remembered that scenario that I saw when I walked in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I recalled that-- I think I was 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father always gave me books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a bookworm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted me to read a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I read a story by-- and-- and-- and that I remember very clearly-- by Alighieri.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was, uh, an Italian poet, and he wrote a book.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he wrote something about And, you know, when I-- when I [INAUDIBLE] it, and I said to myself, if was bad, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and look at this, it must've been a picnic to be in because all he described is that the people working down there with-- with no shirt on, just pants.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they're shoveling coal in intense heat, and that's hell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is worse than hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we, uh-- we, uh-- we went down there, and we went to, uh, uh, eh, appellplatz, where people used to be counted sometimes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were executions were [? placed. ?] And then we had to, uh-- we walked into a building.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We dropped all our clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, uh, our heads were shorn, and, uh, we went, uh, through it at a table down there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Oh, we received, uh, two pieces of cloth, uh, which had a number on there, which is my number, 62 oh 22, and, uh, the insignia, that, uh-- the Magen David, red and yellow.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went through the t-- and we were numb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You understand what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What impression?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Numb.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Completely empty.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
